                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4410" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0624</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9205 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徽商银行：以科技金融创新赋能科创企业发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HUISHANG BANK: science and technology financial innovation to enable the development of science and technology innovation enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王琼，杨如，庄德林</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">合肥工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徽商银行</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徽商银行；科创企业；科技金融；投贷联动</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HUISHANG BANK；Science and technology enterprises；Science and technology finance；Linkage of Investment and Loan</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，伴随着国家“创新驱动发展战略”的实施，科创企业异军突起，然而由于轻资产、规模小、无抵押等特点，科创企业面临较为严峻的融资难问题。作为服务安徽这一科技大省经济发展的地方主流银行，徽商银行已经在探索科技金融的道路上迈出了先行先试的脚步，并已逐步发展成为科技兴皖的金融尖兵。本案例从徽商银行开展科技金融业务的原因切入，全面描述了其设立专业化科技支行、打造定制化贷款产品、开展平台化风险管理、深化投贷联动业务的科技金融创新发展之路。本案例旨在引导学生基于对科技金融概念及构成体系的理解，分析徽商银行开展科技金融业务的动因、创新性举措与面临的挑战，从而加深学生对商业银行科技金融发展的组织架构、业务流程、产品创新、风险控制等全环节的理解。同时，徽商银行科技金融的创新发展对其它商业银行发展科技金融也具有重要的借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, with the implementation of the national &quot;innovation-driven development strategy&quot;, science and technology innovation enterprises have emerged as a new force. However, due to the characteristics of asset-light, small scale and unsecured, science and technology innovation enterprises are faced with severe financing problems. As a local mainstream bank serving the economic development of Anhui province, a big province of science and technology, HUISHANG BANK has taken the lead in exploring the path of science and technology finance, and has gradually developed into a financial leader in science and technology. This case starts from the reasons why HUISHANG BANK carries out science and technology finance business, and comprehensively describes the innovative development path of science and technology finance by establishing specialized science and technology branch, building customized loan products, carrying out platform risk management and deepening the operation of investment and loan linkage. This case is to guide students based on the understanding of financial concept and constitute a system of science and technology, analysis of HUISHANG BANK to carry out financial business of science and technology, innovative measures and challenges, so as to deepen the student to the commercial bank financial development of science and technology organization structure, business process and product innovation, risk control and so on the understanding of all links. At the same time, the innovation and development of science and technology finance of HUISHANG BANK can be used as a reference for other commercial banks to develop science and technology finance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《金融机构经营管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“商业银行贷款经营与管理、商业银行风险控制”</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
